{"title":"本部临时售卖点","icon":"shop","shareable":true,"id":"guide/shop/benbu-temp","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"title","text":"临时购买点"},{"tag":"text","text":["报到期间，本部天猫超市外西北角处 (靠近报到处) 会有临时售卖点。","超市的促销区也会有设置新生用品售卖处。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/shop/benbu-temp1.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/shop/benbu-temp2.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/shop/benbu-temp3.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"title","text":"被褥"},{"tag":"ul","header":"被褥价格","text":["褥子 薄 80左右 厚 150左右","三件套 100 左右","褥子和被子 200+"]},{"tag":"text","type":"note","text":["校园内共有三家在售卖，可以自己对比。","如果卖没了会后续补货。"]}],"time":"2024 年 8 月 16 日 05:53:04"}